{"code":0,"message":"","data":null,"sentence":{"phonemes":[],"text":"Then there is no need to deceive yourself any longer. The mushroom's laughter is a lie you tell yourself. The cat's silence is the only moment you were truly honest. The magician is dead. His spell is buried in the earth with him. But I still remember your true form—","words":[]}}
